SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">2</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">6</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">元旦期间，混元模型升级引入了实时通话能力，首次将“角色来电”从概念变成现实——宣发数据显示，超过3000位观众在节日节点接通了由分身发起的新年电话。用户反馈中，绝大多数表示接到来电时产生强烈的“剧情穿越”感与情绪共鸣，这一体验直接转换为社交平台的二次传播与话题热度。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">和林屿森、聂曦光的“新年的第一通电话”重新定义AI IPbot交互方式，</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">腾讯</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">混元构建了专为角色扮演优化的语音通话架构：</span></span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">●</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">前端ASR精准捕捉用户情感语调</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">；</span></span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">●</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">中控RolePlay LLM 具备极强的语境维持与剧情演绎能力</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">；</span></span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">●</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">后端TTS实现1:1 角色原声复刻</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">；</span></span></span></p>\n  <p><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这套方案解决了传统模型‘像机器、易遗忘’的痛点，拒绝OOC（出戏），确保角色在语音通话中逻辑严密、人设不倒，给粉丝提供影视级的高沉浸互动体验。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"846\" data-backw=\"441\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz_jpg/9u3YmmgmjbTzHz5gianFrMWeBO81HUAictxXiaG9PnshGzfa2rWJVcggK23jayPMbuxsqPGDGupLtrcUotTKFjRpA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"1206.0000000000002\" data-cropy1=\"308.80276816608995\" data-cropy2=\"2622.737024221453\" data-imgfileid=\"100013513\" data-ratio=\"1.9187396351575456\" style=\"margin-left:9.00236px;margin-top:-143.005px;width:100%;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1206\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=44bbc9b1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F9u3YmmgmjbTzHz5gianFrMWeBO81HUAictn8nQeFdpeKcOzdfxGVZArXgOuVveQGf3KW9BrC6GcMfNLqtk2N9gYA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></span></p>\n  <p><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在与剧情节点的联动设计上，宣发团队选择了与剧中情感线高度贴合的场景触点进行玩法开发。以“捏雪人”这一高光浪漫段落为例，站内上线“林屿森为你捏雪人”的互动玩法：用户上传雪人造型或个人照片，AI分身据此生成定制化的“林屿森手作”雪人图像与语音寄语。该活动吸引了10万+剧粉参与，产出的UGC作品在微博、小视频平台与剧区讨论页形成广泛传播，既强化了用户个人情感记忆，也为剧集带来了可持续的讨论热度与口碑裂变。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"236\" data-backw=\"133\" data-imgfileid=\"100013515\" data-ratio=\"1.7777777777777777\" width=\"240.233\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" height=\"427.081\" style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:0px;width:100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c7aeccd2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F9u3YmmgmjbTzHz5gianFrMWeBO81HUAictHuozWLVdegcuYWUS94rx0SkM49bF90RlqX9bQ6jBsyK9ojRGShhLdw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"428\" data-backw=\"240\" data-imgfileid=\"100013512\" data-ratio=\"1.7787037037037037\" width=\"240.381\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" height=\"427.573\" style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:0px;width:100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=122c945c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F9u3YmmgmjbTzHz5gianFrMWeBO81HUAictPrHPsIMmXmVy36CCHqXbeqEL2WJenmGQHnpEylbq2ibtZlC7FLLDEhQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">《骄阳似我》播出期间，剧集热度与社会影响力持续攀升。数据显示，该剧热度值最高达30130，刷新2024年来腾讯视频现偶剧热度纪录；微博开分9.1，创微博评分现偶史上第一；豆瓣开分7.4，创2025年以来国产现代爱情剧最高分。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">随着剧集热播，主创团队也通过直播等形式与观众持续互动，在剧情节点复刻经典名场面，进一步放大剧集讨论热度，形成创作者与观众之间的良性互动。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在内容热度的带动下，《骄阳似我》还引发了显著的文旅联动效应。剧中取景地与剧情发生地受到广泛关注，无锡、苏州、上海、长白山、敦煌等多地文旅机构相继围绕剧集内容推出主题打卡与联动玩法。长白山文旅结合剧中情节整理推出多条“同款路线”，涵盖雪原、咖啡馆、餐饮与家庭出游场景，成为冬季出行的热门选择。上海、敦煌、苏州、无锡等地也通过城市地标、公共空间与剧情彩蛋的方式参与互动，将剧集中的情感记忆延展至现实场景，掀起全民打卡热潮。</span></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "腾讯视频利用混元大模型为热播剧《骄阳似我》打造 AI 角色分身，实现实时语音通话与沉浸式互动，开创了影视宣发的新范式。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "腾讯视频利用混元大模型为热播剧《骄阳似我》打造 AI 角色分身，实现实时语音通话与沉浸式互动，开创了影视宣发的新范式。",
  "summary": "本文介绍了腾讯视频在剧集《骄阳似我》宣发中首次应用 AI 实时通话技术。基于腾讯混元大模型，平台构建了“林屿森”与“聂曦光”两位主角的 AI 分身，通过 ASR、RolePlay LLM 及 TTS 技术栈，实现了 1:1 角色原声复刻与极强的语境维持能力。观众不仅能接听角色发起的“新年电话”，还能参与“捏雪人”等深度联动玩法。这种 AI IPbot 交互方式有效解决了传统模型易出戏（OOC）的痛点，显著提升了粉丝的参与度与情感共鸣，并带动了剧集热度及相关文旅产业的联动效应。",
